@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_yothyc(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.sin((v0 + 0.35 / tmp + 0.31)) - wp.cos(wp.exp(v0 + 0.36)))
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.cos((v0 + 0.38 / v2 + 0.78)))
    v1 = (wp.cos(0.69) - ((v2 + 0.86 - v2 + 0.46) / wp.exp(tmp + 0.94)))
    v2 = (wp.abs(wp.cos(tmp + 0.87)) * (wp.exp(v0 + 0.11) + v1))
    v0 = (((v2 + 0.35 / tmp + 0.59) / v1) - wp.exp(wp.sin(tmp + 0.72)))
    tmp = (wp.cos((v1 + 0.65 - tmp + 0.73)) + wp.cos(wp.abs(v1 + 0.08)))
    data[tid] = v0
